      "content": "i cant even sleep anymore. i just lie there thinking about how everything is basically already over. the tipping points are happening, the oceans are dying, and we’re all just... pretending like we have a future to plan for? it feels so stupid to even try to care about a career or a house or anything when the planet is just a burning wreck. it feels like we're all just waiting for the lights to go out.",
